Description: Generate tables, listings, and graphs (TLG) using
    'tidyverse'.  Tables can be created functionally, using a standard TLG
    process, or by specifying table and column metadata to create generic
    analysis summaries.  The 'envsetup' package can also be leveraged to
    create environments for table creation.
License: Apache License 2.0
URL: https://pharmaverse.github.io/tidytlg/main/,
    https://github.com/pharmaverse/tidytlg
